name: Desigirl-NSFW
description:
Noticed that most models produce either non-Indian looking women, or if prompted, produce very dark skin tones, which some, but not all Indian women have. This textual inversion tries to address that. This model produces photo-realistic women with Indian skin-tone, facial features, and body types.

v2 is trained with a larger number of images allowing for more flexibility and is my recommended inversion, unless there's a reason you like the older one.

Suggested settings are in the "About this version".

Produces NSFW images unless used with very low weightages, or forced through prompts like ((clothed)).

A safe for work version of the model can be found here: https://civitai.com/models/63747/desi-dressed

modelVersions.name: v2.0
modelVersions.description:
Updated version of my most popular download. This version of the textual inversion is built with a much larger data set of over 200 pictures. The quality shows.

Like the previous version - this generates NSFW images, unless heavily suppressed through positive and negative prompts.

Recommended settings:

  1. CFG: 7

  2. Steps: 20

  3. Sampler: Euler a

  4. Weight: 0.5-1 (lower weights produce less pronounced features, and hence creates a variety of 'looks').

Comments/ suggestions welcome
